about.summary: Super State Machine gives you utilities to build finite state machines.

name: super_state_machine
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "super_state_machine" %}
{% set version = "2.0.2" %}
{% set sha = "e038a4c573ab80f157bf726c3036367919704f62cd166eb46837143165035958" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  fn: super_state_machine-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha }}

build:
  number: 1000
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python
    - enum34  # [py2k]
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - super_state_machine

about:
  home: https://github.com/beregond/super_state_machine
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: Super State Machine gives you utilities to build finite state machines.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ericdill
    - licode
    - tacaswell
    - CJ-Wright
